quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  28,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  28,1,toy seen meem
  28,2,yeh kitaab Mubin ki ayaat hain
  28,3,hum moose aur firaon ka kuch haal theek theek tumhe sanatay hain aisay logon ke faiday ke liye jo imaan layein
  28,4,"waqea yeh hai ke firaon ne zameen mein sar kashi ki aur is ke bashindon ko garohoon mein taqseem kar diya un mein se aik giroh ko woh zaleel karta tha, is ke larkoon ko qatal karta aur is ki larkiyon ko jeeta rehne deta tha fi al waqea woh mufsid logon mein se tha"
  28,5,aur hum yeh iradah rakhtay thay ke meharbani karen un logon par jo zameen mein zaleel kar ke rakhay gay thay aur inhen peshwa bana den aur unhi ko waris banayen
  28,6,aur zameen mein un ko Iqtidaar bakhsheen aur un se firaon o Haman aur un ke lashkaron ko wohi kuch dikhla den jis ka inhen dar tha
  28,7,"hum ne moose ki maa ko ishara kya ke"" iss ko doodh pila, phir jab tujhe uss ki jaan ka khatrah ho to usay darya mein daal day aur kuch khauf aur gham nah kar, hum usay tairay hi paas wapas le ayen ge aur is ko payghambaroon mein shaamil karen ge """
  28,8,"aa خرکار firaon ke ghar walon ne usay ( darya se ) nikaal liya taakay woh un ka dushman aur un ke liye Sabab ranj banay, waqai firaon aur Haman aur is ke lashkar ( apni tadbeer mein ) barray ghalat car thay"
  28,9,"firaon ki biwi ne ( is se ) kaha"" yeh mere aur tairay liye aankhon ki thandak hai, usay qatal nah karo, kya ajab ke yeh hamaray liye mufeed saabit ho, ya hum usay beta hi bana len"" aur woh ( injaam se ) be khabar thay"
  28,10,udhar moose ki maa ka dil ura ja raha tha woh is raaz ko faash kar bithti agar hum is ki dhaaras nah bandha dete taakay woh ( hamaray waday par ) imaan laane walon mein se ho
  28,11,uss ne bachay ki behan se kaha is ke peechay peechay ja chunancha woh allag se is ko is terhan dekhatii rahi ke ( dushmanon ko ) is ka pata nah chala
  28,12,"aur hum ne bachay par pehlay hi dُodh pilanay valyon ki chhatiyan haraam kar rakhi theen ( yeh haalat dekh kar ) uss larki ne unn se kaha"" mein tumhe aisay ghar ka pata batau jis ke log is ki parwarish ka zmmh len aur kher khawahi ke sath usay rakhen? """
  28,13,"is terhan hum moose ko is ki maa ke paas palta laaye taakay is ki ankhen thandhi hon aur woh ghamgeen nah ho aur jaan le ke Allah ka wada sacha tha, magar aksar log is baat ko nahi jantay"
  28,14,"phir jab moose apni poori jawani ko poanch gaya aur is ka nashonuma mukammal ho gaya to hum ne usay hukum aur ilm ataa kya, hum naik logon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain"
  28,15,"( aik roz ) woh shehar mein aisay waqt mein daakhil howa jabkay ehley shehar ghaflat mein thay wahan is ne dekha ke do aadmi lar rahay hain aik is ki apni qoum ka tha aur dُosra is ki dushman qoum se talluq rakhta tha is ki qoum ke aadmi ne dushman qoum walay ke khilaaf usay madad ke liye puraka moose ne is ko aik ghonsa mara aur is ka kaam tamam kar diya ( yeh harkat sarzad hotay hi ) moose ne kaha"" yeh shetan ki karfrmayi hai, woh sakht dushman aur khula gumraah kin hai """
  28,16,"phir woh kehnay laga"" ae mere rab, mein ne apne nafs par bara zulm kar dala, meri mughfirat farma day"" chunancha Allah ne is ki mughfirat farma di, woh ghafoor Raheem hai"
  28,17,"moose ne ehad kya ke"" “ay mere rab, yeh ahsaan jo to ne mujh par kya hai iss ke baad ab mein kabhi mujrimon ka madad gaar nah banon ga """
  28,18,"doosray roz woh subah saweray darta aur har taraf se khatrah bhanpta howa shehar mein ja raha tha ke yakayak kya daikhta hai ke wohi shakhs jis ne kal usay madad ke liye puraka tha aaj phir usay pukaar raha hai moose ne kaha"" too to bara hi b_hka howa aadmi hai """
  28,19,"phir jab moose ne iradah kya ke dushman qoum ke aadmi par hamla kere to woh pukaar utha"" ae moose, kya aaj to mujhe usi terhan qatal karne laga hai jis terhan kalshakhs ko qatal kar chuka hai, to is malik mein jabbar ban kar rehna chahta hai, islaah nahi karna chahta """
  28,20,"is ke baad aik aadmi shehar ke parlay siray se Dorta howa aaya aur bola"" moose, sardaro mein tairay qatal ke mashwaray ho rahay hain, yahan se nikal ja, mein tera kher khuwa hon """
  28,21,"yeh khabar suntay hi moose darta aur sehemta nikal khara howa aur is ne dua ki ke"" ae mere rab, mujhe zaalmon se bacha """
  28,22,"( misar se nikal kar ) jab moose ne mudin ka rukh kya to uss ne kaha"" umeed hai ke mera rab mujhe theek rastay par daal day ga """
  28,23,"aur jab woh mudin ke kunwein par pouncha to uss ne dekha ke bohat se log apne janwaron ko pani pila rahay hain aur un se allag aik taraf do aurtain apne janwaron ko rok rahi hain moose ne inn aurton se poocha"" tumhe kya pareshani hai ?"" unhon ne kaha"" hum apne janwaron ko pani nahi pila sakteen jab taq yeh charwahay apne janwar nikaal kar nah le jayen, aur hamaray waalid aik bohat boorhay aadmi hain """
  28,24,"yeh sun ko moose ne un ke janwaron ko pani pila diya, phir aik saaye ki jagah ja betha aur bola"" parvar-digaar, jo kher bhi to mujh par nazil kar day mein is ka mohtaaj hon """
  28,25,"( kuch der nah guzri thi ke ) un dono aurton mein se aik sharam o haya se chalti hui is ke paas aayi aur kehnay lagi"" mere waalid aap ko bُla rahay hain taakay aap ne hamaray janwaron ko pani jo pilaya hai is ka ajar aap ko den"" moose jab is ke paas pouncha aur apna sara qissa usay sُnaya to is ne kaha"" kuch khauf nah karo, ab tum zaalmon se bach niklay ho """
  28,26,"un dono aurton mein se aik ne apne baap se kaha"" abba jaan, is shakhs ko nokar rakh lijiye, behtareen aadmi jisay aap mulazim rakhen wohi ho sakta hai jo Mazboot aur amanat daar ho """
  28,27,"is ke baap ne ( moose se ) kaha"" mein chahta hon ke apni inn do baityon mein se aik ka nikah tumahray sath kar dun bashart e kay tum aath saal taq mere haan mulazmat karo, aur agar das saal poooray kar do to yeh tumhari marzi hai mein tum par sakhti nahi karna chahta tum inn shahAllah mujhe naik aadmi pao ge """
  28,28,"moose ne jawab diya"" yeh baat mere aur aap ke darmain tey ho gayi un dono muddaton mein se jo bhi mein poori kar dun uss ke baad phir koi zayad-ti mujh par nah ho, aur jo kuch qoul qarar hum kar rahay hain Allah is par nigehbaan hai """
  28,29,"jab moose ne muddat poori kar di aur woh apne ahal o Ayal ko le kar chala to tor ki janib is ko aik aag nazar aayi uss ne apne ghar walon se kaha"" tehromein ne aik aag dekhi hai, shayad mein wahan se koi khabar le aon ya is aag se koi angara hi uttha lau jis se tum tap sakuu """
  28,30,"wahan pouncha to waadi ke dahinay kinare par mubarak khittay mein aik darakht se puraka gaya ke"" ae moose, mein hi Allah hon, saaray Jahan walon ka maalik """
  28,31,"aur ( hukum diya gaya ke ) pheink day apni laathi jounhi ke moose ne dekha ke woh laathi saanp ki terhan bil kha rahi hai to woh peeth phair kar bhaga aur is ne murr kar bhi nah dekha ( irshad howa )"" moose, palat aa aur khauf nah kar, to bilkul mehfooz hai"
  28,32,"apna haath garibaan mein daal, chamakta howa niklay ga baghair kisi takleef ke aur khauf se bachney ke liye apna baazu bhinch le yeh do roshan nishanain hain tairay rab ki taraf se firaon aur is ke drbaryon ke samnay paish karne ke liye, woh barray hi nafarman log hain """
  28,33,"moose ne arz kya"" mere aaqa, mein to un ka aik aadmi qatal kar chuka hon, darta hon ke woh mujhe maar dalain ge"
  28,34,"aur mera bhai haroon mujhe se ziyada zabaan aawar hai, usay mere sath madad gaar ke tor par bhaij taakay woh meri taied kere, mujhe andesha hai ke woh log mujhejjhutlainge """
  28,35,"farmaya"" hum tairay bhai ke zareya se tera haath mazboot karen ge aur tum dono ko aisi Satwat bakhsheen ge ke woh tumhara kuch nah bigaar saken ge hamari nishanion ke zor se ghalba tumhara aur tumahray pairwon (mannay walon ka) ka hi ho ga """
  28,36,phir jab moose unn logon ke paas hamari khُli khُli nishanain le kar pouncha to unhon ne kaha ke yeh kuch nahi hai magar banawati jadugar aur yeh baatein to hum ne apne baap dada ke zamane mein kabhi sُnin hi nahi
  28,37,"moose ne jawab diya"" mera rab uss shakhs ke haal se khoob waaqif hai jo is ki taraf se hadaayat le kar aaya hai aur wohi behtar jaanta hai ke aakhri injaam kis ka acha hona hai, haq yeh hai ke zalim kabhi Falah nahi paate """
  28,38,"aur firaon ne kaha"" ae ahal darbaar mein to apne siwa tumahray kisi khuda ko nahi jaanta Haman , zara eenten pkwa kar mere liye aik onche imarat to banava, shayad ke is par charh kar mein moose ke khuda ko dekh sakun, mein to usay jhoota samjhta hon """
  28,39,uss ne aur is ke lashkaron ne zameen mein baghair kisi haq ke apni barayi ka ghamand kya aur samjhay ke inhen kabhi hamari taraf palatna nahi hai
  28,40,aakhir-kaar hum ne usay aur is ke lashkaron ko pakra aur samandar mein pheink diya ab dekh lau ke un zaalmon ka kaisa injaam howa
  28,41,hum ne inhen jahannum ki taraf dawat dainay walay paish ro bana diya aur qayamat ke roz woh kahin se koi madad nah pa saken ge
  28,42,hum ne iss duniya mein un ke peechay laanat laga di aur qayamat ke roz woh barri qabahat mein mubtala hon ge
  28,43,"pichli naslon ko halaak karne ke baad hum ne moose ko kitaab ataa ki, logon ke liye basiraton ka samaan bana kar, taakay shayad log sabaq haasil karen"
  28,44,"( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) tum uss waqt maghribi gooshay mein mojood nah thay jab hum ne moose ko yeh farmaan Shariat ataa kya, aur nah tum shahideen mein shaamil thay"
  28,45,"balkay is ke baad ( tumahray zamane taq ) hum bohat si naslen utha chuke hain aur un par bohat zamana guzar chuka hai tum ehley mudin ke darmain bhi mojood nah thay ke unn ko hamari ayaat suna rahay hotay, magar ( uss waqt ki yeh khabrain ) bhejnay walay hum hain"
  28,46,"aur tum tor ke daman mein bhi uss waqt mojood nah thay jab hum ne ( moose ko pehli martaba ) puraka tha, magar yeh tumahray rab ki rehmat hai ( ke tum ko yeh maloomat di jaar hi hain ) taakay tum unn logon ko mutnabba kar do jin ke paas tum se pehlay koi mutnabba karne wala nahi aaya, shayad ke woh hosh mein ayen"
  28,47,"( aur yeh hum ne is liye kya ke ) kahin aisa nah ho ke unn ke apne kiye krtoton ki badolat koi museebat jab unn par aeye to woh kahin"" ae parvar-digaar, too ne kyun nah hamari taraf koi rasool bheja ke hum teri ayaat ki pairwi karte aur ehley imaan mein se hotay """
  28,48,"magar jab hamaray haan se haq un ke paas aa gaya to woh kehnay lagey"" kyun nah diya gaya iss ko wohi kuch jo moose ko diya gaya tha ?"" kya yeh log uss ka inkaar nahi kar chuke hain jo is se pehlay moose ko diya gaya tha? unhon ne kaha"" dono jadugar hain jo aik doosray ki madad karte hain"" aur kaha"" hum kisi ko nahi mantay """
  28,49,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ) un se kaho,"" acha to lao Allah ki taraf se koi kitaab jo inn dono se ziyada hadaayat bakhsnay wali ho agar tum sachey ho, mein isi ki pairwi ikhtiyar karoon ga """
  28,50,"ab agar woh tumhara yeh mutalba poora nahi karte to samajh lau ke darasal yeh apni khwahisaat ke pairo hain, aur uss shakhs se barh kar kon gumraah ho ga jo khudai hadaayat ke baghair bas apni khwahisaat ki pairwi kere? Allah aisay zaalmon ko hargiz hadaayat nahi bakhshta"
  28,51,aur ( nasiyaat ki ) baat pay Dur pay hum inhen pouncha chuke hain taakay woh ghaflat se beedar hon
  28,52,jin logon ko is se pehlay hum ne kitaab di thi woh iss ( quran ) par imaan laatay hain
  28,53,"aur jab yeh unn ko sُnaya jata hai to woh kehte hain ke"" hum iss par imaan laaye, yeh waqai haq hai hamaray rab ki taraf se, hum to pehlay hi se muslim hain """
  28,54,yeh woh log hain jinhein un ka ajar do baar diya jaye ga uss saabit qadmi ke badlay jo unhon ne dikhayi woh buraii ko BHALAI se dafaa karte hain aur jo kuch rizaq hum ne inhen diya hai is mein se kharch karte hain
  28,55,"aur jab unhon ne behooda baat suni to yeh keh kar is se kinara kash ho gay ke"" hamaray aamaal hamaray liye aur tumahray aamaal tumahray liye, tum ko salam hai, hum jahilon ka sa tareeqa ikhtiyar nahi karna chahtay """
  28,56,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum jisay chaho usay hadaayat nahi day satke, magar Allah jisay chahta hai hadaayat deta hai aur woh un logon ko khoob jaanta hai jo hadaayat qubool karne walay hain"
  28,57,"woh kehte hain"" agar hum tumahray sath iss hadaayat ki pairwi ikhtiyar kar len to apni zameen se uchak liye jayen ge"" kya yeh waqea nahi hai ke hum ne aik pur aman haram ko un ke liye jaye qiyam bana diya jis ki taraf har terhan ke smrat khche chalay atay hain, hamari taraf se rizaq ke tor par? magar un mein se aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  28,58,"aur kitni hi aisi bastiyan hum tabah kar chuke hain jin ke log apni maeeshat par Itra gay thay so dekh lau, woh un ke maskan parre hue hain jin mein un ke baad kam hi koi basa hai, akhirkar hum hi waris ho kar rahay"
  28,59,aur tera rab bustiyon ko halaak karne wala nah tha jab taq ke un ke markaz mein aik rasool nah bhaij deta jo un ko hamari ayaat sunataa aur hum bustiyon ko halaak karne walay nah thay jab taq ke un ke rehne walay zalim nah ho jatay
  28,60,"tum logon ko jo kuch bhi diya gaya hai woh mehez duniya ki zindagi ka samaan aur is ki zeenat hai, aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai woh is se behtar aur baqi tar hai kya tum log aqal se kaam nahi letay ?"
  28,61,bhala woh shakhs jis se hum ne acha wada kya ho aur woh usay panay wala ho kabhi is shakhs ki terhan ho sakta hai jisay hum ne sirf hayaat duniya ka srosaman day diya ho aur phir woh qayamat ke roz saza ke liye paish kya jaane wala ho ?
  28,62,"aur ( bhool nah jayen yeh log ) uss din ko jab ke woh inn ko pukare ga aur pouchye ga"" kahan hain mere woh shareek jin ka tum gumaan rakhtay thay? """
  28,63,"yeh qoul jin par chaspan ho ga woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, be shak yahi log hain jin ko hum ne gumraah kya tha, aِnhin hum ne usi terhan gumraah kya jaisay hum khud gumraah hue hum aap ke samnay bara'at ka izhaar karte hain yeh hamari to bandagi nahi karte thay """
  28,64,phir inn se kaha jaye ga ke poukaro ab apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko yeh inhen pukaarain ge magar woh inn ko koi jawab nah den ge aur yeh log azaab dekh len ge kash yeh hadaayat ikhtiyar karne walay hotay
  28,65,"aur ( faramosh nah karen yeh log ) woh din jabkay woh inn ko pukare ga aur pouchye ga ke"" jo rasool beje gay thay inhen tum ne kya jawab diya tha? """
  28,66,uss waqt koi jawab inn ko nah sughay ga aur nah yeh aapas mein aik doosray se pooch hi saken ge
  28,67,Albata jis ne aaj tauba kar li aur imaan le aaya aur naik amal kiye wohi yeh tawaqqa kar sakta hai ke wahan Falah panay walon mein se ho ga
  28,68,"tera rab peda karta hai jo kuch chahta hai aur ( woh khud hi apne kaam ke liye jisay chahta hai ) muntakhib kar laita hai, yeh intikhab inn logon ke karne ka kaam nahi hai, Allah pak hai aur bohat balatar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
  28,69,tera rab jaanta hai jo kuch yeh dilon mein chupaye hue hain aur jo kuch yeh zahir karte hain
  28,70,"wohi aik Allah hai jis ke siwa koi ibadat ka mustahiq nahi isi ke liye hamd hai duniya mein bhi aur akhirat mein bhi, farmaa rawai isi ki hai aur isi ki taraf tum sab pultay jaane walay ho"
  28,71,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho kabhi tum logon ne ghhor kya ke agar Allah qayamat taq tum par hamesha ke liye raat taari kar day to Allah ke siwa woh konsa mabood hai jo tumhe roshni laa day? kya tum suntay nahi ho ?"
  28,72,"inn se pucho, kabhi tum ne socha ke agar Allah qayamat taq tum par hamesha ke liye din taari kar day to Allah ke siwa woh konsa mabood hai jo tumhe raat laa day taakay tum is mein sukoon haasil kar sakuu? kya tum ko sujhta nahi ?"
  28,73,"yeh isi ki rehmat hai ke is ne tumahray liye raat aur din banaye taakay tum ( raat mein ) sukoon haasil karo aur ( din ko ) apne rab ka fazl talaash karo, shayad ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
  28,74,"( yaad rakhen yeh log ) woh din jabkay woh inhen pukare ga phir pouchye ga"" kahan hain mere woh shareek jin ka tum gumaan rakhtay thay? """
  28,75,"aur hum har ammt mein se aik gawah nikaal layein ge phir kahin ge ke"" lao ab apni Daleel "" is waqt inhen maloom ho jaye ga ke haq Allah ki taraf se hai, aur gum ho jayen ge un ke woh saaray jhoot jo unhon ne ghurr rakhay thay"
  28,76,"yeh aik waqea hai ke qaroon moose ki qoum kashakhs tha, phir woh apni qoum ke khilaaf sarkash ho gaya aur hum ne is ko itnay khazanay day rakhay thay ke un ki knjyan taaqat war admion ki aik jamaat mushkil se uttha sakti thi aik dafaa jab is ki qoum ke logon ne uss se kaha"" phool nah ja, Allah phoolnay walon ko pasand nahi karta"
  28,77,"jo maal Allah ne tujhe diya hai is se akhirat ka ghar bananay ki fikar kar aur duniya mein se bhi apna hissa faramosh nah kar ahsaan kar jis terhan Allah ne tairay sath ahsaan kya hai aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa karne ki koshish nah kar, Allah mfsdon ko pasand nahi karta """
  28,78,"to uss ne kaha"" yeh sab kuch to mujhe uss ilm ki bana par diya gaya hai jo mujh ko haasil hai"" kya is ko ilm nah tha ke Allah is se pehlay bohat se aisay logon ko halaak kar chuka hai jo is se ziyada qowat aur jamiat rakhtay thay? mujrimon se to un ke gunah nahi pouchye jatay"
  28,79,"aik roz woh apni qoum ke samnay apne poooray thaath mein nikla jo log hayaat duniya ke taalib thay woh usay dekh kar kehnay lagey"" kash hamein bhi wohi kuch milta jo qaroon ko diya gaya hai, yeh to bara naseebay wala hai """
  28,80,"magar jo log ilm rakhnay walay thay woh kehnay lagey"" afsos tumahray haal par, Allah ka sawab behtar hai uss shakhs ke liye jo imaan laaye aur naik amal kere, aur yeh doulat nahi millti magar sabr karne walon ko """
  28,81,aakhir-kaar hum ne usay aur is ke ghar ko zameen mein dhansa diya phir koi is ke hamion ka giroh nah tha jo Allah ke muqaabla mein is ki madad ko aata aur nah woh khud apni madad aap kar saka
  28,82,"ab wohi log jo kal is ki manzilat ki tamanna kar rahay thay kehnay lagey"" afsos, hum bhool gay thay ke Allah apne bundon mein se jis ka rizaq chahta hai kushadah karta hai aur jisay chahta hai npa tala deta hai agar Allah ne hum par ahsaan nah kya hota to hamein bhi zameen mein dhansa deta afsos hum ko yaad nah raha ke kafir Falah nahi paaya karte """
  28,83,woh akhirat ka ghar to hum unn logon ke liye makhsoos kar den ge jo zameen mein apni barayi nahi chahtay aur nah fasaad karna chahtay hain aur injaam ki BHALAI muttqeen hi ke liye hai
  28,84,"jo koi BHALAI le kar aeye ga is ke liye is se behtar BHALAI hai, aur jo buraii le kar aeye to buraiyan karne walon ko waisa hi badla miley ga jaisay amal woh karte thay"
  28,85,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yaqeen jano ke jis ne yeh quran tum par farz kya hai woh tumhe aik behtareen injaam ko pohanchanay wala hai inn logon se keh do ke"" mera rab khob jaanta hai ke hadaayat le kar kon aaya hai aur khُli gumraahi mein kon mubtala hai """
  28,86,"tum is baat ke hargiz umeed waar nah thay ke tum par kitaab nazil ki jaye gi, yeh to mehez tumahray rab ki meharbani se ( tum par nazil hui hai ), pas tum kafiroon ke madad gaar nah bano"
  28,87,aur aisa kabhi nah honay paye ke Allah ki ayaat jab tum par nazil hon to KUFAR tumhe unn se baz rakhen apne rab ki taraf dawat do aur hargiz mushrikon mein shaamil nah ho
  28,88,aur Allah ke sath kisi doosray mabood ko nah poukaro uss ke siwa koi mabood nahi hai har cheez halaak honay wali hai siwaye uss ki zaat ke farmaa rawai usi ki hai aur usi ki taraf tum sab pultay jao ge
